      "id": "P_ON_EACH_RISING_RDY_CROSSING_SAMPLE",
      "observable_contract": "On each rising `rdy` crossing, sample `din0..din5` with switched weights `0.5, 1, 2, 4, 8, 16` from `din0` through `din5`. Map the sampled weighted code to a bipolar single-ended output scaled by `vdd` using this public normalization:",
